    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>Hi, I'm Abdul Raheem Mohammed. I am pursuing a Masters (Master of Science - MS in Project Management). At the helm of operations at 73rd Solution Inc., my focus is on refining customer relationship management systems to enhance client development strategies. My educational pursuit of a Master of Science in Project Management at Cumberland University fortifies my ability to orchestrate complex operations within the organization.</p>
        <p>With a background in mechanical engineering and a progressive career from Talent Acquisition Specialist to Business Development Manager, my approach is rooted in a technical understanding of industry demands. We leverage this insight to foster robust global talent acquisition, ensuring our clients access premier professionals seamlessly.</p>
